channel.title: I can't put my server online? Not sure why?
channel.description:
Ok I know to get servers online you need to make a No-ip from No-ip.com. You also need to port forward 43594. I have had previous servers so I already had 43594. I tried getting into the No-ip I had made(by getting into my no-ip, I mean getting into my server using the no-ip), but it didn't work. any help?
-Thanks

dont use 127.0.0.1 go to start and click run
when it loads type cmd and then click enter
then when that page loads type ipconfig and try using the first 1 and use all of them if the 1st one dont work
